rules:
  # Product specification rule
  - requires: ["./docs/product_spec.md"]
    prompt: |
      Always reference `./docs/product_spec.md` for product features, user stories,
      and acceptance criteria. Use this when deciding *what* to build or how a feature
      should behave from the product perspective.

  # Technical specification rule
  - requires: ["./docs/tech_spec.md"]
    prompt: |
      Always reference `./docs/tech_spec.md` for implementation details, architecture,
      and code-level requirements. Use this when deciding *how* to build the features
      or what technical changes are needed.
